<br />
<br />While I don't have much experience in writing emulators, I'm willing to give it a go.  But I wondered, since foo_gep uses Game_Music_Emu and foo_gep plays both MMC5 and VRC7 fine, has this been done already?  And if so can I have access to those patches/source files?

		

